<br>
Kazadun, if you check out the first page, somewhere in the initial comments, someone posted the stats on the True Silver Idol. It's Magic and Lore, but NOT No Drop, so there is hope <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukayshasoulsinger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaysha Soulsinger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/14/01 5:27:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3421.topic&index=155>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: More Tenebrous Named</span><hr size=1> When analyzing the list of Jewels needed by the various classes, a few interesting observations can be made.<br>
<br>
First of all it appears that every time two armor pieces are connected in what Jewels are needed.<br>
<br>
Boots - on their own<br>
Bracers - Weapon<br>
Breastplate - Cloak<br>
Gloves - Sleeves<br>
Helm - Veil<br>
Shoulders - Belt<br>
Greaves - Neck<br>
<br>
Also, the Jewel scheme of several Classes is coinciding<br>
<br>
Bard - Wizard<br>
Magician - Beastlord - Monk<br>
Druid - Paladin<br>
Rogue - Enchanter<br>
Necromancer - Warrior<br>
Cleric - Ranger<br>
Shadowknight - Shaman<br>
<br>
However, there are a few discrepancies in this list. First of all, the Necromancer list appears to be the same as the Warrior one, but half of it is unknown. Secondly, there appears to be a deviation in two classes from this scheme, Rangers and Wizards. It might be a good idea to double-check those ...<br>
<br>
With Rangers, the list currently says Moon Jewel for the Belt and Sun Jewel for the Axe, but according to the &quot;general&quot; plot, the Axe should have the Moon Jewel, and the Belt the Sun Jewel.<br>
<br>
Also, the Wizard has Cloud Jewel listed for the Mask, while this - according to the general layout - should be the Meteor Jewel.<br>
<br>
All the others confirm to the general scheme for the Jewels. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3946.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3951.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3421.topic&index=155><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3421.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3421.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3421.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3421.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesaf